<br>
    On the other hand, people who demand outrageous amounts of money for a service they are capable of providing are also being rude themselves.  I have seen some of the prices some people will charge for their spells that don't have material components or high mana costs, and I just shake my head in disgust.  But then charging 100pp for a rez that costs a stinking peridot and some mana (yes, I know it's a healthy amount of mana, but then, so are ports)  I think is unjustified.  50pp?  More reasonable.<br>
<br>
   Anyways, that's just my 2cp worth.<br>
