<br>
IMHO, it is more than just mana, its time, and if someone is spending their time playing taxi (or catapult, for wizards <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ), I feel its only right that I pay them.  I almost always head to whomever offers to port me, and on the occasions I don't, there's a valid reason.  I can honestly say nothing like the DL incident has occured on those occasions, but if it had, I would most certainly get a rez for the person, as well as compensate them (as I'm sure a majority of people on this server would do).<br>
